WEBVTT

00:00.553 --> 00:03.220
Reverie, a virtual reality program

00:03.222 --> 00:05.222
where the impossible becomes possible.

00:05.842 --> 00:08.575
Anything you desire you can find here.

00:09.088 --> 00:11.295
But sometimes, people get lost,

00:11.297 --> 00:13.998
caught between fantasy and reality.

00:14.000 --> 00:15.499
That's where she comes in.

00:15.501 --> 00:17.801
Her name is Mara Kint.

00:17.803 --> 00:21.906
Her job, find the lost ones
and bring them home.

00:21.908 --> 00:24.575
And maybe by saving them,

00:24.577 --> 00:28.078
she just might find a way
to save herself.

00:28.080 --> 00:36.166
Synced & corrected by -robtor-
www.addic7ed.com

00:37.270 --> 00:38.770
Previously on "Reverie"...

00:38.805 --> 00:40.539
- I know you're in danger.
- What kind of danger?

00:40.573 --> 00:41.940
Losing your mind.

00:41.974 --> 00:43.975
Is Oliver right? Am I going to go crazy?

00:44.010 --> 00:46.912
Oliver was unstable
long before he got a BCI.

00:46.946 --> 00:49.214
Stop, no!

00:49.248 --> 00:51.483
I got shot. Should I be worried?

00:51.517 --> 00:52.751
I'm really sorry, by the way,

00:52.785 --> 00:54.586
that I didn't return your calls.

00:54.620 --> 00:56.288
The calls I made 19 months ago?

00:56.322 --> 00:57.389
I've been thinking about you.

00:57.423 --> 00:59.424
Can we talk later?

